For the morons who cannot read the info file:
1: Torrent the damn thing

2: Should have three objects (1 Folder labeled Cracks, 1 FL Installer, 1 Notpad file labeled Info)
BE SURE YOUR INTERNET IS OFF!

3: Install FL to whatever your heart's desire but UNCLICK run, so when you click finish, it does not run.

4: After install go into the "Cracks" folder, then go into the FL folder on your computer. Should be easy, my computer > C: > Program Files > Image-Line

5: After finding the FL folder, go into "FL Studio 9" and copy the FL Crack from the cracks folder, to the FL Studio folder. REMEMBER: Copy and REPLACE the files.

6: After doing so, go into the folders marked "Poizone" and copy that crack into the "Poizone" folder in the install directory.

7: Do the same thing for the other cracks, except be sure to match name with folder.

8: After getting everything right, be sure to re-boot as a "Just-in-case" factor. (It's what I do, I never have problems)

9: If you do not get this? Too damn bad.
